graph LR
    subgraph PyTorch Training Loop
        A[Forward Pass] --> B[Loss Calculation]
        B --> C[Metric Calculation: F1/AUC]
        
        C -.->| writer.add_scalar | D(SummaryWriter)
        C -.->| writer.add_figure | D
    end
    
    D -->| Writes to disk: ./runs/ | E[(Log Events Database)]
    
    subgraph Browser Frontend
        F[TensorBoard Server] -->| Reads ./runs/ | E
        F --> G[Live Dashboard UI]
    end
    
    style D fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#fbc02d
    style E fill:#eceff1,stroke:#607d8b
    style G fill:#ffccbc,stroke:#d84315
